title: Tove Lo
itunes:title: Tove Lo
description:
Singing, songwriting, directing (now acting!) genius Tove Lo is on the show this week and she is as magical as she seems. In addition to her groundbreaking work, she and Whitney discuss soulmates, sexy granny panties, comedic porn, and why there aren’t any strip clubs in Norway. They also get into Tove’s four minute masturbation scene in her short film Fairy Dust. Tove's 4th studio album Sunshine Kitty is out now and she recently made her feature film acting debut in The Emigrants. Her CANN line of THC infused drink Passion Peach Maté is available now.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
